name: EMERGENCY: The Paramedic Simulation
blurb: The game that puts a player in real life situations and emergencies that a paramedic or emt face everyday.

rewards.reward: A big thanks for your support and you will have access to download EMERGENCY:TPS screen saver or digital copies of concept art.

For this support you receive a full version of the game in either: iPad, iPhone, Android, PC or MAC. Name on list of "Thank You for your Support" page of the official website, and access to screen savers and some music from the game.
For this support, you will receive access to the beta version of the game on either PC or MAC. You will also receive all the above rewards.

For this level of support you will receive all the above rewards and have access to the beta forums. In these forums, you can comment on problems and submit ideas on how to improve game play. You will also receive an EMERGENCY:TPS plastic paramedic badge.

This is the Silver level of support, and at this level your name will be listed in the Silver Support thank you section on the official game website. You will also receive an official EMERGENCY:TPS t-shirt in your size, digital copy of official artwork for the game, and a digital copy of the soundtrack for the game.

This is the Gold Level of support, and you will receive a hardcover copy of the limited edition Art of EMERGENCY:TPS, and a limited edition, one time print, of your choice from the book. It will be signed by the artist as well. Your name will be listed in the thank you section for Gold Level of support and you will also receive all the above rewards.

This is the Platinum Level of support, and was designed for a organization or person that wants to help create a patient. I will use a photo of choice to make the patients face, let you decided the patient's name, and the patient's condition and symptoms. This is a great way to teach future EMS personnel and medical professionals about your organization. You will also receive a link to your website in the game, advertisement on the official game website, and a plaque thanking you for your support. This also includes all the above rewards and your name listed in the Platinum support thank you section on the website.

Here is the ultimate package for the company or person that wants to promote their ambulance company, hospital, helicopter, fire service to future EMS people or the general layperson. With this pledge you will get your company name or your name on the ambulance going to the call, fire truck on the call, the helicopter landing and taking off from the call, police vehicles, and the Hospital building the ambulance crew goes to. There are only so many of these and yes, that means your company name will be seen multiple times. You will also receive a plaque with your name or your company's name. This pledge includes advertisement space on the official Emergency:TPS website that links to your website. All the above gifts are also included in the package, including your name in the game on the list of Platinum contributors in the credits.

This level is called the EMERGENCY:TPS Partner. At this level of support you have officially become a co-producer of the game. You will be included in any meetings of your choice in development and will be kept in the loop by me. I will use you as resource and you will be able to help in anyway you would like. You will get all the above rewards and will be part of the team, so your name will be on the website and video game as a co-producer. You will also be invited to any events regarding the game.
